graph TB
    subgraph "Feast Feature Store Component"
        Operator[Feast Operator<br/>Go Kubernetes Operator]
        Online[Online Feature Store<br/>Python Service<br/>6566-6567/TCP]
        Offline[Offline Feature Store<br/>Python Service<br/>8815-8816/TCP]
        Registry[Registry Server<br/>Python gRPC/REST<br/>6570-6571/TCP]
        UI[UI Server<br/>Python Web Service<br/>8888/8443/TCP]
        CronJob[Materialization CronJob<br/>Scheduled Tasks]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| FeatureStoreCR[FeatureStore CR<br/>feast.dev/v1alpha1]
    FeatureStoreCR -->|watched by| Operator

    Operator -->|creates & manages| Online
    Operator -->|creates & manages| Offline
    Operator -->|creates & manages| Registry
    Operator -->|creates & manages| UI
    Operator -->|creates & manages| CronJob

    subgraph "Storage Backends"
        Redis[(Redis<br/>Low-latency KV Store)]
        PostgreSQL[(PostgreSQL<br/>Persistent DB)]
        S3[(S3/GCS<br/>Object Storage)]
    end

    Online -->|reads/writes| Redis
    Online -->|reads/writes| PostgreSQL
    Online -->|queries metadata| Registry

    Offline -->|reads historical data| S3
    Offline -->|queries metadata| Registry

    Registry -->|persists to| PostgreSQL
    Registry -->|persists to| S3

    CronJob -->|materializes features| Online
    CronJob -->|fetches from| Offline

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collection]
        OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>OIDC Provider]
        CertManager[cert-manager<br/>TLS Certs]
    end

    Operator -->|manages resources| K8sAPI
    Operator -->|exposes metrics| Prometheus
    Online -.->|optional auth| OpenShiftOAuth
    Offline -.->|optional auth| OpenShiftOAuth
    Registry -.->|optional auth| OpenShiftOAuth
    UI -.->|optional auth| OpenShiftOAuth
    Operator -.->|requests certs| CertManager

    subgraph "Client Applications"
        MLApp[ML Application<br/>Real-time Inference]
        TrainingJob[Training Job<br/>Batch Processing]
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Discovery UI]
    end

    MLApp -->|POST /get-online-features| Online
    TrainingJob -->|POST /get-historical-features| Offline
    Dashboard -->|browses features| UI

    style Operator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Online fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Offline fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Registry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style UI fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style FeatureStoreCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Redis fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style PostgreSQL fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style OpenShiftOAuth fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333
